Note:
Runa Scientific Computing: Interactive Plotting

Advanced interactive visualization capabilities surpassing matplotlib widgets,
plotly, and bokeh with real-time updates and rich user interactions.

Features:
- Interactive widgets (sliders, buttons, dropdowns, text inputs)
- Real-time data updates and streaming plots
- Zoom, pan, select, and brush interactions
- Linked views and cross-filtering
- Animation and time-series playback
- Custom callbacks and event handling
- WebGL-accelerated rendering for large datasets
- Multi-touch and gesture support
- Dashboard layouts with responsive design
- Export to interactive web formats
:End Note

Import "scientific/plotting/core" as PlotCore
Import "scientific/core/ndarray" as NDArray
Import "../../collections" as Collections
Import "../../string" as String
Import "math/core" as Math

