    tail as Integer

Process called "update_streaming_data" that takes streaming_plot as StreamingPlot and new_data as NDArray.NDArray:
    add_to_buffer with buffer as streaming_plot.data_buffer and data as new_data
    update_plot_from_buffer with streaming_plot as streaming_plot
    If streaming_plot.auto_scale:
        auto_scale_axes with subplot as streaming_plot.subplot and buffer as streaming_plot.data_buffer

Process called "create_real_time_callback" that takes figure as InteractiveFigure and update_function as Function[Float, NDArray.NDArray] and interval_ms as Integer returns UpdateCallback:
    Let callback be UpdateCallback with:
        callback as function that takes timestamp as Float returns Any:
            Let new_data be update_function with timestamp
            trigger_data_update with figure as figure and data as new_data
        trigger_events as list containing "timer"
        data_dependencies as list containing
    Add callback to figure.update_callbacks
    start_timer_callback with callback as callback and interval as interval_ms
    Return callback

