Process called "create_default_toolbar" returns InteractiveToolbar:
    Let tools be list containing
    Add create_tool with type as ZoomTool to tools
    Add create_tool with type as PanTool to tools
    Add create_tool with type as SelectTool to tools
    Add create_tool with type as ResetTool to tools
    Add create_tool with type as SaveTool to tools
    Return InteractiveToolbar with:
        tools as tools
        active_tool as None
        position as Top
        orientation as Horizontal
        style as create_default_toolbar_style()

Process called "create_tool" that takes type as ToolType returns Tool:
